      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, maintained to a standard rarely seen outside of a showroom. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free from any swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings, having been protected by a high-grade ceramic coating and stored exclusively in a climate-controlled garage. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather seats show no signs of creasing or wear, and the original 'new car' scent is still subtly present. Every electronic feature, from the adaptive cruise control to the premium sound system, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by certified technicians using OEM parts. It drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the lot\u2014tight, responsive, and exceptionally smooth. Included are all original keys, the complete owner\u2019s manual set, and a folder of detailed maintenance records. This is an investment-grade example for the most discerning collector or enthusiast.",
      "price": 44800.0,
